-Fisher, R. A. (1956), *Statistical Methods and Scientific Inference*, Oliver & Boyd, London.
-Jaynes, E. T. (1976), "Confidence Intervals vs Bayesian Intervals", in *Foundations of Probability Theory, Statistical Inference, and Statistical Theories of Science*, W. L. Harper and C. A. Hooker, eds., Reidel, Dordrecht, pp. 175-257.
-Jeffreys, H. (1939), *Theory of Probability*, Oxford University Press.
-Lindley, D. V. (1958), "Fiducial Distribution and Bayes' Theorem", *J. Roy. Stat. Soc. B* **20**, 102-107.
